column5: Will drop 6+ cents after midnight.  Still getting it
Were suppose to feel better, 6 cents. Man, do they think were stupid. 80 cents wouldn't be asking to much. The media has already told them to put it up for the weekend.
146.9 this morning in Montreal.143.9 this afternoon.132.6 on the reserve.137.8 at Costco.Who has the real price of gas Does the real price of gas even exist?
WOW! 132 is sooooo cheap, can't wait to pay that tomorrow... geez
well I guess all I can do is hope the natives win a land claim in Bradford, so we get reserve prices
If you had status that might work but you still pay tax man. Unless you have friends.  There's nothing you can do about it. Well I guess complaining is something. They should bring back the Moped.
My new to me car is not that great on gas but boy does it look cool.
Moped, yeah they were ,,interesting.........  I am real glad I have a diesel now 15 cents a liter less then gas prices

Funny how gas drops down my way.  $3.95 this morning and $4.09 this evening.  UNBELIEVABLE.   Glad my neighbor said he saw one station at $4.09 and the others still at $3.95.  So, a quick trip to the gas station before the others raised there.  93 bucks later - full tank.
been 125 in cobourg for the whole time ...
125 in peterborough, but 140 in newcastle..........how does that work again???  I'm so glad I run super......
1.41 in aurora....I'll believe it when I see it!
I got "gas" for $108.41 tonight..  Jack Astors @ Yonge/Dundas! Where Jennifer wanted to go and I wasn't gonna stop the effort to walk there!
thanks for the laugh Wayne.  You are absolutely correct and I feel so proud of Jennifer....what a strong young woman....and she makes me cry.
The price of gas is going up and down faster then Tiger Woods underoos and golf scores
